<h1>
<a href="https://www.politico.com/news/2019/12/08/north-korea-rocket-weapon-test-078015" target="_top">North Korea conducts ‘important test’ at once-dismantled site</a></h1>
<p class="subhead">President Donald Trump reacted to the development by saying that North Korea “must denuclearize.”</p>
</header>
<footer class="meta">
<footer class="meta">
<div itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
<meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press" />
<meta itemprop="email" content="" />
