<p class="subhead">Diplomatic ties between the countries have been in statis since the February breakdown of a second summit.</p>
</header>
<footer class="meta">
<footer class="meta">
<div itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
<meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press" />
<meta itemprop="email" content="" />
