<h1>
<a href="https://www.politico.com/story/2019/08/05/north-korea-missiles-fired-1448837" target="_top">As talks stall, North Korea launches again</a></h1>
</header>
<footer class="meta">
<footer class="meta">
<div itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
<meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press" />
<meta itemprop="email" content="" />
